        <description>&lt;img src="http://0.0.0.0:1313/homepage-denied.png" alt="Featured image of post HOMEPAGE_ALLOWED_HOSTS env parameter" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;So you&amp;rsquo;ve landed here because your getting an error like this in your &lt;code&gt;homepage.dev&lt;/code&gt; logs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
